[[:Category:red| Red ]] : This category is used for keeping track of the '''''[[Glossary#Skills| Skills]]''''' of characters AND the '''''[[Glossary#Features| Features]]''''' of starships.  However, starships currently do not have any red-features because this would overlap with torpedo (high-damage) weapons.  Thus this catagory will only contain references to [[:category:crew| crew]].
