== Summary == Level 50 is one of the primary goals for leveling up any character... Level 50 is the maximum level for a [[:Category:Tier 1]] character or starship...
There are several aspects to this page, but for now i just want to put it here as a placeholder... * making Lvl-50 character pages, like [[CO/L50/CK]], [[CO/L50/AK]], and [[CO/L50/KN]] * tier-1 crew and/or ships can become level-50 once '''10''' evolutions and some dilithium are spent on them... * tier-2 crew and/or ships also become level-50 once '''10''' evolutions and some dilithium are spent on them... * however, tier-3 crew and/or ships can become level-50 after only '''''3''''' evolutions and some dilithium are spent on them...
