== Summary == Level 95 is one of the primary goals for leveling up any character... Level 95 is the maximum level for a [[:Category:Tier 2]] character or starship...
There are several aspects to this page, but for now i just want to put it here as a placeholder... * making Lvl-95 character pages, like [[CO/L95/AK]], [[CO/L95/AR]], [[CN/L95/KG]], and [[CN/L95/CLF]] * tier-2 crew and/or ships can become level-95 once 15 evolutions and some dilithium are spent on them... * making '''Lvl-96''' character pages, like [[CO/L96/KN]], [[CN/L96/B3]] * tier-3 crew and/or ships become level-96 once 9 evolutions and some dilithium are spent on them... ** we use the end of the 9th evolution for [[:Category:Tier 3]] items, because it is easier-to-calculate... ** while the pages, themselves, are labelled (correctly) for L96; the category for these pages will still be [[:category:level95]] ...
== Upgrades ==
