== Three versions ==

* {{color|blue|text=Blue = Easy}}
* {{color|yellow|text=Yellow = Normal}}
* {{color|purple|text=Purple = Legendary}}

All three versions use the same storyline about a [[Federation]] station with a surprising survivor and unlikely enemies.

For further descriptions of the three versions, see: [[Events in general#Three versions]]

{{EventText02|13|6}}

=== Storyline ===
Storyline summary per mission...
For a description of the storyline-chart, see: [[Events in general#Storyline]]
==== Trivia ====
* in the storyline, they use the actor-name (antonio) rather than the character-name ([[Arden]]) in some places.  (eg. lvl-11)
