== Description ==
:This template is for autotyping an introductory sentence on every character or starship page.

;Syntax
:<code>{{t|side|name-to-use|tier-#|Crew-or-Ship|TOS-or-TNG}}</code>

== Samples ==
* <pre>{{side}}</pre> gives ==> {{side}}
* <pre>{{side||1|}}</pre> gives ==> {{side||1|}}
* <pre>{{side|Kirk|2|c|o}}</pre> gives ==> {{side|Kirk|2|c|o}}
* <pre>{{side|Data|1|c|n}}</pre> gives ==> {{side|Data|1|c|n}}
* <pre>{{side|Enterprise-B|3.5|s|o}}</pre> gives ==> {{side|Enterprise-B|3.5|s|o}}
* <pre>{{side|Blah-Blah|200|X|Y}}</pre> gives ==> {{side|Blah-Blah|200|X|Y}}

<includeonly>[[Category:General wiki templates|{{PAGENAME}}]]</includeonly><noinclude>[[Category:Template documentation|{{PAGENAME}}]]</noinclude>

== Description ==
:This template is used in the introductory section for most every character or starship page.  It mainly creates a context-link to the Memory-Alpha Wiki so that the reader can learn some more information.

;Syntax
:<code>{{t|ma|PAGENAME for link on Memory-Alpha wiki}}</code>

== Samples ==
* <pre>{{ma|Enterprise}}</pre> gives ==> {{ma|Enterprise}}
* <pre>{{ma|USS Enterprise (NCC-1701)}}</pre> gives ==> {{ma|USS Enterprise (NCC-1701)}}
* <pre>{{ma|Unnamed Humans (23rd century)}}</pre> gives ==> {{ma|Unnamed Humans (23rd century)}}

<includeonly>[[Category:General wiki templates|{{PAGENAME}}]]</includeonly><noinclude>[[Category:Template documentation|{{PAGENAME}}]]</noinclude>

== Description ==
:This template is used for ''PICKING'' a single gem color out of a listing of the six-colors for a character in their infoboxes.  It is used within the diplomacy-values section of the infobox for a character.

;Syntax
:<code>{{t|GemOrdered|six initials for colors, in Left-to-Right order|position-to-pick}}</code>

See also: {{t|GemSix}}

== Samples ==
* <pre>{{GemOrdered}}</pre> gives ==> {{GemOrdered}}
