== Three versions ==

* {{color|blue|text=Blue = Easy}}
* {{color|yellow|text=Yellow = Normal}}
* {{color|purple|text=Purple = Legendary}}

All three versions use the same storyline about a [[Borg]] mining facility from the future and [[Q]]'s trial of the Enterprise crew when they are forced to interfere ;  {{EventText02|15|4}} 

