== Overall Prizes ==

Each version has a series of overall prizes that can be earned as you accumulate the points for each mission-win...  

=== Common Objectives ===
these mind meld prizes are gained thru all the players combining their scores within each series...
* Easy = 35,000,000 combined points (not 50m)
** {{P|g|100|g}}
** {{P|d|2000|x}}
** {{P|b|1|b}} (not 2)
** {{ships|nch}}
* Normal = 65,000,000 combined points (not 140m)
** {{P|g|300|g}}
** {{P|d|5000|x}}
** {{P|b|1|b}} (not 4)
** {{ships|nch}}
** 1 [[Borg 1 of 4]]
* Legendary = 90,000,000 combined points (not 220m)
** {{P|g|600|g}}
** {{P|d|10000|x}}
** {{P|r|1|r}}
** 1 [[Borg 2 of 4]]
** 1 [[Borg 1 of 4]]
==== Trivia ====
* easy only 1 (not 2) basics...
* normal only 1 (not 4) basics...
ck=e1-5/m1-5/h1-5



=== Rewards-Prizes ===
these prizes are solo efforts, by accumulating points in each series...
==== '''Easy''' ====
Baseline score for winning all the missions ''once'' is 4725 points.  ''(lost 25 points at lvl-11.5)''
Full score for earning all the mission-prizes using 1 hr skips between wins per mission is 18,900 points.  Need to repeat higher-scoring missions to reach the last ''one'' reward level...
==== '''Normal''' ====
Full score for earning all the mission-prizes using 1 hr skips between wins per mission is 37,800 points.  Need to repeat higher-scoring missions to reach the last ''two'' reward levels...
==== '''Legendary''' ====
Full score for earning all the mission-prizes using 1 hr skips between wins per mission is 56,700 points.  Need to repeat higher-scoring missions to reach the last ''three'' reward levels...
==== Trivia ====
* tbd...
