== Overall Prizes ==

Each version has a series of overall prizes that can be earned as you accumulate the points for each mission-win...  

=== Common Objectives ===
these mind meld prizes are gained thru all the players combining their scores within each series...
* Easy = 50,000,000 combined points
** {{P|g|100|g}}
** {{P|d|2000|x}}
** {{P|b|2}}
** 1 [[SO/KBP]]
* Normal = 140,000,000 combined points
** {{P|g|300|g}}
** {{P|d|5000|x}}
** {{P|b|4}}
** 1 [[Salt Vampire]]
** 1 [[SO/KBP]]
* Legendary = 220,000,000 combined points
** {{P|g|600|g}}
** {{P|d|10000|x}}
** {{P|r|1}}
** 1 [[Horta]]
** 1 [[Ruk]]



=== Rewards-Prizes ===
these prizes are solo efforts, by accumulating points in each series...
==== '''Easy''' ====
Baseline score for winning all the missions ''once'' is 4750 points.  
Full score for earning all the mission-prizes using 1 hr skips between wins per mission is 19,000 points.  Need to repeat higher-scoring missions to reach the last ''one'' reward level...

