{{Disambig}}
Ferengi is a race of [[:Category:Alien|aliens]] who are not quite as prolific in the [[:Category:TNG|TNG]] universe as the klingons, romulans, or cardassians.  However, they are [[:Category:TNG Crew|playable characters]] available for manning the occasional [[:Category:TNG Ship]] , specifically the [[Marauder]].  Alternatively, maybe you just want the primary-page of [[:Category:Ferengi]].
[[Category:Ferengi]]

