{{#invoke:EventTables|main|Storyline
|C444|Preparations|En route to system Sense, the crew of the Enterprise prepares for their encounter with the "Tychon" and "Veau", two races that inhabit this system and find themselves in the midst of a global crisis.  They are being decimated by a deadly virus.
|S444|SOS|While Picard explains the mission, the Enterprise receives a distress call from an Andorian Shuttle.
|B333|C|.
|D444|Secrets|After rescuing the Andorian, Picard must determine exactly what has occurred.
|S444|First meet|Picard prepares for his meeting with the interlocuters.
|D444|Negotiations|In the designated neutral zone, tense negotiations have begun to find a solution for the epidemic.
|B444|S|.
|D332|Suspicions|Upon returning to the ship, Picard analyzes the situation and establishes a plan of action.
|B433|C|.
|S444|Second meeting|Picard discusses the ship's condition with La Forge.
|C444|Investigation|Riker continues the investigation where Thira left off.
|D333|The laboratory|Riker investigates the cave's interior.
|B444|S|.
|C444|The prison|Inside the cave they hear voices.
|D444|Question of confidence|Meanwhile, in the infirmary of the Enterprise.
|C444|The return|Picard transports the leaders kidnapped from both races.
|B333|S|.
|C433|Treason|Riker follows Thira back to the cave.
|S444|Final meeting|The Romulans finally show themselves.
}}

